description:
Digital edition of the He-Man & Masters of Universe: Minicomic Collection hardcover omnibus split into two digital collections.

THE MOST POWERFUL STORIES IN THE UNIVERSE! The toy juggernaut Masters of the Universe and its subsequent action figure lines featured memorable pack-in minicomics that aided in playtime for children across the world. This two volume digital collection features sixty-eight US releases, including all minicomics from the eighties Masters of the Universe line, the eighties Princess of Power line, and the eighties and nineties He-Man line, plus an introduction to the minicomics in the current Masters of the Universe Classics toy line. Relive the illustrated adventures that fueled your imagination!
name: He-Man & Masters of Universe: Minicomic Collection

description:
An All-New, All-Different Marvel series. Spinning out of the pages of Avengers Vol.5 and Secret Wars comes an all-new team of Avengers. Perhaps not mightiest, but surely the most dedicated! The series lasted for only 15 issues due to the events of Civil War II, after which the younger heroes formed their own group in Champions Vol. 2 and the old guard continued their adventures in Avengers Vol.6. The series had one All-New, All-Different Avengers Annual.

Collected Editions

  • All-New, All-Different Avengers: The Magnificent Seven (#1-6)
  • Timely Comics: All-New, All-Different Avengers (#1 (Story A Only) & #2-3)
  • Avengers: Standoff (#7-8)
  • All-New, All-Different Avengers: Family Business (#7-12)
  • All-New, All-Different Avengers: Civil War II (#13-15)
name: All-New, All-Different Avengers
